Parameters:-->
		Also called as functional parameters or Method parameters
		=> Parameters change state of method behaviour
		
		Advantages of parameters:-->
			=> Method reusability[Instead of duplicating methods
				we can use same method with different input values]
				
			=> Data flexibility [User can change any time data from 
				outside fo the class]
				
			=> Avoid hardcoding 
			
		Parameters types:-->
			CallByValue
			CallByReference
			
		CallByValues:--> Passing Datatypes as parameters like
				[String,int,boolean,double,floag,char ---etc]
				
				
				public class Browser
				{
					 public void Open(String browsername)
					 {
					 	System.out.prinln(browsername);
					 }
					 
					 public static void main(String args[])
					 {
					 		Browser obj=new Browser();
					 		obj.Open("chrome");
					 }
				}
				
				
				
				
				
				
				
				
				
				
				
				
				